OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMayhill riot: South Wales  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FPolice response criticised 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fin independent review      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police have been criticised over their 
OL,6, handling of a riot which broke out in  
OL,7, Swansea, in an independent review that 
OL,8, said residents were left "unprotected".
OL,10,FCars were burnt and windows smashed in 
OL,11,Fthe Mayhill area after a vigil to a    
OL,12,Fyoung man who had died turned violent. 
OL,14,FEthan Powell's father Jonathan Russ    
OL,15,Flater condemned those who rioted at his
OL,16,Fson's vigil in May 2021, calling them  
OL,17,F"scumbags".                            
OL,19,FSouth Wales Police has now apologised  
OL,20,Ffor its slow response.                 
